{"type":"message","id":"257a2149","parentId":"316c002d","timestamp":"2026-04-01T01:31:11.854Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_psa9h9oPm9Tukbr8E4Xn1sAR","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 2026-03-27: 建立 crypto/CRON_RULES.md，定义主巡检/高频轻巡检/宏观事件巡检三层 cron 的分工、共享上下文、触发条件、输出格式与冲突优先级。\n- 2026-03-27: 已将 crypto 巡检拆分为三条 cron：主巡检（Crypto main scan V1）、高频轻巡检（Crypto fast risk scan）、宏观/事件巡检（Crypto macro event scan）。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775007071851}}
